   "source": [
    "# Reporting: figures\n",
    "\n",
    "This module is the core for the production of the images that can be used for visually assessing the price data.\n",
    "\n",
    "All package figures are based on `BaseFigure` object that offers basic methods for working with matplotlib figures."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "The autoreload extension is already loaded. To reload it, use:\n",
      "  %reload_ext autoreload\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "%load_ext autoreload\n",
    "%autoreload 2\n",
    "from surfingcrypto import Config,TS\n",
    "from surfingcrypto.reporting.figures import SimplePlot,TaPlot,ATHPlot"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Then load the configuration files."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "coins={\n",
    "    \"BTC\":\"\",\n",
    "    \"ETH\":\"\",\n",
    "    \"MATIC\":\"\",\n",
    "    \"ADA\":\"\",\n",
    "    \"SOL\":\"\"\n",
    "}\n",
    "c = Config(coins,\"/Users/giorgiocaizzi/Documents/GitHub/surfingcrypto/config\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### The `TaPlot` figure"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Produce a comples `ta` plot for each coin specified in the configuration file."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "BTC plotted.\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1500x1500 with 5 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ts.ta_indicators()\n",
    "tap=TaPlot(\n",
    "    object=ts,\n",
    "    graphstart=\"6m\"\n",
    "    )"
   ]
  },
